These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, domino, poker, chess, snooker, scrabble, billiard
7 different pets are kept: frog, goat, goldfish, lizard, mouse, rat, snake
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the frog is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing chess##1
10. the person playing chess is the owner of the goat##1
11. the person playing chess is between the owner of the goldfish and the person playing poker##2
12. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| Game   | scrabble  | chess | poker  | snooker | backgammon | domino | billiard |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat   | snake | lizard  | rat   | mouse    | frog    |

