.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, skiing, golf, biathlon, ice-hockey, cricket
There are 7 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, mexican, nigerian, polish, russian, spanish
 1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the polish##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the russian is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the mexican is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 8. the person who's sport is golf is between the polish and the colombian##2
 9. the nigerian is on the right of the mexican##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
11. the chinese is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Sport      | skiing | golf | ice-hockey   | basketball | cricket | baseball     | biathlon |
| Nationality   | colombian     | chinese  | polish | russian     | spanish  | mexican | nigerian |

