 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the snake##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking cola##1
 9. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |     3      |      4      |      5      |       6       |     7      |
| Beverage   | sprite  | almond-milk | water | fanta | tea | lemonade | cola    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | snake   | bird       | hamster     | ferret      | rat           | chinchilla |

