The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, hip-hop, metal, r&b, rock, salsa
 1. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 2. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the wooden house##1
 5. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the futuristic house is between the fan of salsa and the fan of r&b##2
 7. the art-deco house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the fan of rock is the tower house##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the victorian house##1
11. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
12. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
13. the fan of dubstep is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |   2   |       3        |  4   |     5      |    6    |      7       |
| House           | tower | art-deco | ranch-style | futuristic | craftsman | victorian   | wooden |
| Music-Genre   | rock            | metal | r&b            | d&b  | salsa      | hip-hop | dubstep      |

