The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, car, jet-ski, roller, scooter, ship, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the car##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the car is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in april##2
10. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |     4      |     5     |    6    |    7    |
