 6. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 7. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing monopoly and the person watching superhero movies##2
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
11. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama         | family | epic   | crime        | superhero  | romance  | horror |
| Game         | canasta | go  | whist | bridge | scrabble | mah-jongg | monopoly |

