.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, orchid, daisy, daffodil, zinnia, begonia
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, horror, mystery, scientific, thriller
 1. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growsdaisy##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |    5    |      6       |      7      |
| Flower           | daisy | azalea   | daffodil | orchid    | aconite   | begonia | zinnia     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | action | horror        | adventure | mystery | scientific   | documentary |

 